    <head>RELATED MATERIAL</head>
<p>RMC Collection #51-01-1368. Norman Moore papers, 1919-1994.</p><p> RMC Collection #24-01-119. <extref href="http://resolver.library.cornell.edu/cgi-bin/EADresolver?id=RMA0019" show="new">Veranus A. Moore papers, 1836-1958.</extref></p>  </relatedmaterial>
