<p>Shackleton Family Collection, #37-05-3133. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
  <acqinfo id="aspace_b291a9eeda0130df42eab3b00f00c5ec">
    <head>PROVENANCE</head>
<p>The scrapbooks and film were given to the Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections by the DeWitt Historical Society in 2001. Mary Moore's class notes were separated from the Veranus Moore papers in 2004.</p>  </acqinfo>
